  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "game-theory",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-theory/yunxi/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.01,
      "size": 16128,
      "text": "欢迎来到博弈论实验。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-theory",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-theory/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32400,
      "text": "你有没有想过，为什么两家相邻的加油站价格总是差不多？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-theory",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-theory/yunxi/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29520,
      "text": "或者，为什么国家之间会陷入军备竞赛的困境？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-theory",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-4",
      "filename": "intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-theory/yunxi/intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.74,
      "size": 27792,
      "text": "博弈论正是研究这类策略互动的数学工具。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-theory",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-1",
      "filename": "concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-theory/yunxi/concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.58,
      "size": 25344,
      "text": "博弈论研究的是多个决策者之间的策略互动。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-theory",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-2",
      "filename": "concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-theory/yunxi/concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.31,
      "size": 37008,
      "text": "每个参与者都试图最大化自己的收益，同时考虑其他人的可能行动。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-theory",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-3",
      "filename": "concept-concept-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-theory/yunxi/concept-concept-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.38,
      "size": 38160,
      "text": "核心概念是纳什均衡：没有人能通过单方面改变策略来获得更好的结果。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-theory",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-4",
      "filename": "concept-concept-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-theory/yunxi/concept-concept-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.77,
      "size": 44352,
      "text": "这个概念由约翰·纳什在1950年提出，他因此获得了诺贝尔经济学奖。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-theory",
      "section_id": "prisoner",
      "line_id": "prisoner-1",
      "filename": "prisoner-prisoner-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-theory/yunxi/prisoner-prisoner-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.54,
      "size": 24624,
      "text": "让我们来看最著名的博弈：囚徒困境。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-theory",
      "section_id": "prisoner",
      "line_id": "prisoner-2",
      "filename": "prisoner-prisoner-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-theory/yunxi/prisoner-prisoner-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.03,
      "size": 32544,
      "text": "两个嫌疑人被分开审讯，每人可以选择沉默或背叛对方。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-theory",
      "section_id": "prisoner",
      "line_id": "prisoner-3",
      "filename": "prisoner-prisoner-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-theory/yunxi/prisoner-prisoner-3.mp3",
      "duration": 3.75,
      "size": 60048,
      "text": "如果都沉默，各判1年；都背叛，各判3年；一人背叛一人沉默，背叛者释放，沉默者判5年。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-theory",
      "section_id": "prisoner",
      "line_id": "prisoner-4",
      "filename": "prisoner-prisoner-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-theory/yunxi/prisoner-prisoner-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.27,
      "size": 36288,
      "text": "理性分析表明，双方都会选择背叛，尽管双方沉默对整体更好。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-theory",
      "section_id": "nash",
      "line_id": "nash-1",
      "filename": "nash-nash-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-theory/yunxi/nash-nash-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.59,
      "size": 25488,
      "text": "囚徒困境中的双方背叛就是一个纳什均衡。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-theory",
      "section_id": "nash",
      "line_id": "nash-2",
      "filename": "nash-nash-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-theory/yunxi/nash-nash-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.07,
      "size": 33120,
      "text": "在这个状态下，任何一方单独改变策略都会让自己更糟。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-theory",
      "section_id": "nash",
      "line_id": "nash-3",
      "filename": "nash-nash-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-theory/yunxi/nash-nash-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 30960,
      "text": "纳什均衡不一定是最优结果，但它是一种稳定状态。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-theory",
      "section_id": "nash",
      "line_id": "nash-4",
      "filename": "nash-nash-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-theory/yunxi/nash-nash-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.8,
      "size": 28800,
      "text": "纳什证明了每个有限博弈至少存在一个纳什均衡。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-theory",
      "section_id": "application",
      "line_id": "app-1",
      "filename": "application-app-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-theory/yunxi/application-app-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.21,
      "size": 19296,
      "text": "博弈论在现实中有广泛应用。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-theory",
      "section_id": "application",
      "line_id": "app-2",
      "filename": "application-app-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-theory/yunxi/application-app-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.86,
      "size": 29808,
      "text": "在经济学中，它用于分析市场竞争和拍卖设计。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-theory",
      "section_id": "application",
      "line_id": "app-3",
      "filename": "application-app-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-theory/yunxi/application-app-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.97,
      "size": 31536,
      "text": "在政治学中，它帮助理解国际关系和投票行为。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-theory",
      "section_id": "application",
      "line_id": "app-4",
      "filename": "application-app-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-theory/yunxi/application-app-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.04,
      "size": 32688,
      "text": "在生物学中，它解释了动物的进化策略和合作行为。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-theory",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-theory/yunxi/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.27,
      "size": 20304,
      "text": "今天我们探索了博弈论的基本概念。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-theory",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-theory/yunxi/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29376,
      "text": "博弈论揭示了理性个体如何在互动中做出决策。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-theory",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/game-theory/yunxi/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.88,
      "size": 30096,
      "text": "它告诉我们，个体理性有时会导致集体非理性的结果。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "game-theory",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-4",
